Text.string: Hey, VH! I'm always lookin' for unique car parts. Bring me the sickest war machines you find out in the wild, and I'll make 'em available for you at the Catch-A-Ride!
Hoo, that's a beefy hunk of vehicle right there. Go on and grab it for me.
Holy high-tech hoverwheels! I ain't never seen a technical like that a'fore. What're you waitin' for? Get in!
Righteous! Now bring that super-sick hoverin' monster in to the Catch-A-Ride!
Check out the sweet mine-chucker on that bandit technical! I wants it, VH!
Now drive it on back to the Catch-A-Ride, and I'll scan that sweet weapon in for ya.
Badass! That mine-chucker's all yours if you wanna slap it on a technical next time you Catch-A-Ride!
That fat wheel makes the Cyclone look tough as hell. You definitely want some of that.
Nice grab, VH. Now bring that oversized death-donut back to the Catch-A-Ride!
That fat wheel may not be as fast as the little one, but she can take a beatin' before givin' out.
That thing's got razor wings on it! You gotta get that vehicle for yourself, VH!
Now drive it back to the Catch-A-Ride so I can scan it.
Let's get that sharp-as-hell runner into the Catch-A-Ride system, VH.
Ain't no one gonna run you off the road when you got them razor wings equipped! Now, fly, you razor-strapped raven!
Whoa! There's a sick-ass booster device on that ride right there! Pick it up!
Lookin' forward to gettin' that in the ol' Catch-A-Ride system!
That thing'll drop shock charges behind you while you boost! Sweet!
Ho-damn! You check out the fancy wheels on that ride? Bet you want to get yer hands on that!
Now drive on by the Catch-A-Ride so we can get them wheels in the system!
With them things you're gonna be scootin' around like your life depends on it. Which it prob'ly will.
These are gonna be sick as hell for strafin' around! Go ahead and build you a hoverin' death ride next time you pick up a rig!
Hoo! I scanned that area and picked up a technical with a sick-ass tire launcher on it. Go find it!
Aw, hell yeah! That's some sweet outrunner armor you just nabbed. Give it a try next time you Catch-A-Ride!
Awesome! Now bring it on over to the Catch-A-Ride and let me digiscan that bad boy!
Ready to chuck some tires and light some fires, VH? That tire launcher is now available at all your conveniently-located Catch-A-Rides!
Hey, VH. Know what's even cooler than a booster? A frickin' triple booster! Get me that sweet ride right there! It's behind that barrier!
All right! Good get, VH. Now drive that thing over to your nearest Catch-A-Ride!
Never seen a faster ride in all my days. This'll get you speedin' along like you wouldn't believe. Pick one up and keep hittin' that boost!
Oh, dang, you gotta pick up that fancy Cyclone. That thing's got blink tech for boostin' in style!
Be sure to bring that thing on by the Catch-A-Ride so I can put it in the system.
Shoot! With that fancy blink tech, ain't nobody gon' catch you, VH!
Hoo, check out them zip wheels! Go ahead'n pick up that ride!
Now bring it on home to the Catch-A-Ride and let me give it a scan.
Them zip wheels are the tits for driftin'! And now we can get you rollin' on those bad boys whenever you want, VH!
Holy crap-spackle. Those wheels are bad-to-the-max badass. Go get 'em!
Now bring that hunk of burnin' rubber back to the Catch-A-Ride for me.
Them technicals is gon' look sweet as hell ridin' on those big mamma-jammas. Good find, VH!
